Pass the user's full question as the `query` parameter.

## Priority 3: Direct sources (shell fallback)

```bash
# Product doc indexes
curl -s https://developers.cloudflare.com/llms.txt
curl -s https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/llms.txt
curl -s https://developers.cloudflare.com/r2/llms.txt
curl -s https://developers.cloudflare.com/d1/llms.txt

# Fetch a page as Markdown
curl -sH "Accept: text/markdown" https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/
curl -s https://developers.cloudflare.com/r2/get-started/index.md
```

