## Notes

- Each product publishes an `llms.txt` index with direct Markdown URLs.
- Workers bindings (KV, R2, D1) are configured in `wrangler.toml` / `wrangler.jsonc` — search the relevant product docs for binding syntax.
- `ai` covers Workers AI models and inference; `ai-gateway` covers observability, caching, and routing for external AI providers.
